    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            const ori_total = parseInt($('#section4').data('total'));
            let slider_loop = ori_total >= 3 ? true : false;
            $('#section4').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: slider_loop,
                dummySlide: slider_loop,
				afterSlide: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
					if(slider_loop) {
						if(current_page == ori_total) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2).Slider('start');
						}
						if(current_page == ori_total * 2 + 1) {
							slider.Slider('jump', ori_total + 1).Slider('start');
						}
					}
				},
                afterInit: function(slider, slides, current_page, total_page) {
                    if(slider_loop) {
                        slider.Slider('jump', ori_total * 2);
                    }
                    else {
                        slider.Slider('jump', total_page);
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section6">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">Testimonials</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="tabs">
                                    <button class="tab current" data-id="1">Students</button>
                                    <button class="tab" data-id="2">Parents</button>
                                    <button class="tab" data-id="3">Alumni</button>
                            </div>
            <select class="tab-select" name="tab"><option value="1">Students</option><option value="2">Parents</option><option value="3">Alumni</option></select>                            <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                            <div class="record-slider">
                            <div class="slider-container">
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/1c4e493d611125a3f8e59d349fc1e2b6.png" alt="Untitled design" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>1 / 4</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">I like Peak School because it is a fun and safe place to learn. I think there are a lot of great people here, too. I have found so many friends throughout the years. Peak School also has a lot of good learning opportunities and experiences. I feel safe and happy when I am here. There are also a lot of encouraging teachers and educational assistants. They always teach me when I struggle, especially in maths. There are a lot of good facilities to help us learn. Sometimes I feel frustrated, but I always have friends here to cheer me up! That’s why I like Peak School.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">I like Peak School because it is a fun and safe place to learn. I think there are a lot of great people here, too. I have found so many friends throughout the years. Peak School also has a lot of good learning opportunities and experiences. I feel safe and happy when I am here. There are also a lot of encouraging teachers and educational assistants. They always teach me when I struggle, especially in maths. There are a lot of good facilities to help us learn. Sometimes I feel frustrated, but I always have friends here to cheer me up! That’s why I like Peak School.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Alyssa Ng - Y6 Student -  Class of 2025</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/7c62044cc9dc5e763d35888cdceb2593.png" alt="Untitled design (1)" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>2 / 4</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">I think Peak school is the best school in the world. Why? Because it makes me feel like it’s fine to be myself. It’s a great learning experience, and I guarantee you that you will find amazing teachers, and loads of new friends in this awesome school. I joined in Year 3, and every day, I walk in the same doors and I still feel like I just joined. There are unique people here, and all people with different cultures are welcome. I love this school because it makes me feel like it’s okay to be myself and to be unique. The learning environment in this school is great, too. All the teachers are really nice, and make sure you have fun, even in the subjects you hate. And when you go for playtime, you get to play in a gigantic playground! I  love this school, and I’ll never forget it, even when I’m like 80 or something.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">I think Peak school is the best school in the world. Why? Because it makes me feel like it’s fine to be myself. It’s a great learning experience, and I guarantee you that you will find amazing teachers, and loads of new friends in this awesome school. I joined in Year 3, and every day, I walk in the same doors and I still feel like I just joined. There are unique people here, and all people with different cultures are welcome. I love this school because it makes me feel like it’s okay to be myself and to be unique. The learning environment in this school is great, too. All the teachers are really nice, and make sure you have fun, even in the subjects you hate. And when you go for playtime, you get to play in a gigantic playground! I  love this school, and I’ll never forget it, even when I’m like 80 or something.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Alicia Lau - Y6 Student, Class of 2025</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/e8bcba6a24da17c596acbed2a0ab25fd.jpg" alt="IMG_1747" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>3 / 4</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Learning at Peak School is fabulous. The teachers and all staff are supportive, kind, and caring. Our school is surrounded by greenery, providing great views of nature and wildlife. We even have our own garden. The playground is marvellous, with lots of different types of activities, including my personal favourite, the supernova. There’s lots of room to run about and have fun.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Learning at Peak School is fabulous. The teachers and all staff are supportive, kind, and caring. Our school is surrounded by greenery, providing great views of nature and wildlife. We even have our own garden. The playground is marvellous, with lots of different types of activities, including my personal favourite, the supernova. There’s lots of room to run about and have fun.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Albert Dahlsten - Year 6 Student, Class of 2025</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/769ed03edff2825e3613fabce4a8ad85.png" alt="Untitled design (2)" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>4 / 4</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">What I love about Peak School is that we do fun things, such as celebrating all the different cultures of our community. What I like the most is that we have buddy time to spend with different years, such as Year 4 and Year 1. This is good because we do fun stuff together and play games. We also learn from each other.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">What I love about Peak School is that we do fun things, such as celebrating all the different cultures of our community. What I like the most is that we have buddy time to spend with different years, such as Year 4 and Year 1. This is good because we do fun stuff together and play games. We also learn from each other.</p>
