                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Peak School is the best example of learning in the company of friends. Dedicated faculty, engaged students, a beautiful and spacious property; all of these factors work in harmony to make Peak School the best place for our children Rory (graduate) and Pascale (current student).</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Peak School is the best example of learning in the company of friends. Dedicated faculty, engaged students, a beautiful and spacious property; all of these factors work in harmony to make Peak School the best place for our children Rory (graduate) and Pascale (current student).</p>
