                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Peak School from day 1 has always felt very welcoming and has a great community. My two daughters, Year 2 and Year 4 - are both thriving and more importantly enjoying going to school.  With loads of extracurricular activities and access to world class learning and development, I feel very happy that my girls are receiving a well rounded education.  The teaching staff are excellent, all led superbly by Headmaster Bill Garnett.</p>
