                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/41c5819e7b80774e2f21cfa438f95fff.jpeg" alt="IMG_A91B2AAF70CE-1" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>2 / 3</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Throughout my journey at the school, I heard the phrase: “Exceed your limits, be kind, and go above and beyond”. I often wondered how it would help me grow as a person. Peak School gave me a sense of belonging in the community, which made me understand why it’s so important to be kind to others. The teachers I had always supported me and kept cheering me on - which helped me challenge myself to try new things. The school boosted my confidence; making me a person who encourages and supports others; allowing me to view the world with kindness and care. Peak School, you have a special place in my heart. Thank you for helping me become the person I am today.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
