    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
            
            $('.tab', '#section6').click(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $(this).addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($(this).index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.tab-select', '#section6').change(function() {
                $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div', '#section6').removeClass('current');
                $('.tab-select .select-container div:nth-child(' +  ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').addClass('current');
                $('.select .select-container div', '#section6').show();
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section6').index() + 1) + ')', '#section6').hide();
                chkContentHeight();
            });

            $('.record-slider', '#section6').Slider({
                slides: '.record-item',
                maxSlide: 1,
                swipeControl: true,
                skipBoundary: true,
                infiniteLoop: true
            });

            function chkContentHeight() {
                $('p.description', '#section6').each(function() {
                    if($(this).height() > 160) {
                        $(this).parent().addClass('more');
                    }
                });
            }
            chkContentHeight();

            $('.record-item article button.view-more', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-less').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').show();
            });
            $('.record-item article button.view-less', '#section6').click(function() {
                $(this).hide();
                $(this).parent().find('.view-more').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.description').show();
                $(this).parent().find('.content').hide();
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section7" data-total="10">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What's New at Peak School?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="record-slider">
        <div class="slider-container">
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="132">
                        <time>25/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>✨ At Peak School, children’s safety and well‑being come first. ✨<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>💙 We’re proud to introduce our Child Protection Officers — dedicated staff members assigned to promote student welfare and ensure every child feels safe, supported, and protected from harm.<br><br>🌱This initiative highlights our commitment: child protection isn’t just a policy, it’s a promise. Together with parents and families, we’re building a community where every child can thrive.<br><br>#childprotection #esf #hongkong #wellbeing</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/9493a966ce230a7eb91669d900fdc131.jpg" alt="639741393_17992300613931900_5539395838464427808_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="131">
                        <time>11/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>🎉 Peak School Year 1 just reached an incredible milestone—100 days of school! 🥳 <br>.<br>.<br>.<br>🎊To mark the occasion, our creative and enthusiastic students took the lead in planning their very own celebration!<br><br>🪩From designing the decorations to choosing the snacks, they showed amazing teamwork and independence in bringing the party to life. <br><br>💛It was a joyful day filled with laughter, learning, and pride in how far they’ve come. <br><br>🙏A heartfelt thank you goes out to our wonderful mum volunteers, as well as the Year 1 teachers and EAs, whose support and planning made this event such a memorable success. <br><br>#100dayscelebration #primaryschool #esf #hongkong</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/5d382e0f673814b61bf3ef426d521d24.jpg" alt="627718377_864606476619428_2702695275404846314_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="130">
                        <time>02/02/2026</time>
                        <h3>Say cheese—it’s time for our annual whole-school photo! 📸 <br>.<br>.<br>.<br>💪A huge shoutout to our amazing parent volunteers who braved the early morning to make it all happen. <br><br>🥰Here’s to an incredible 25/26 school year ahead!</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/06bc432844c8ed43ff02465f743a2251.jpg" alt="626642711_1396751611416779_1721071518686695602_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="129">
                        <time>19/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>🍕 Farm-to-Table Fun! 🌱<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>🌾Our Year 3 Peakies had an unforgettable day at the New Zealand Organic Farm in Lam Tseun! <br><br>🍅From harvesting fresh organic veggies straight from the garden to kneading their very own pizza dough, the kids got hands-on with every step of the process. <br><br>✨The best part? Creating delicious pizzas topped with the greens they picked themselves. <br><br>🌿What a wholesome, tasty adventure!<br><br>#schooltrip #farmtotable #pizzamaking #hongkong #esf</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/0bcd560aa672bd1c1cc2b27b0730dd3e.jpg" alt="618064330_17988180917931900_7383467351094736397_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="128">
                        <time>12/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>✨ Another magical year, another unforgettable Peak School Nativity at St. John’s Cathedral! ✨<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>👏We are deeply grateful for the incredible support and contributions that made this year’s Nativity so special. <br><br>❤️Coming together as a community was especially meaningful as we showed our solidarity with the victims of the Tai Po fire tragedy.<br><br>🌟Our students shone brightly on stage—their dedication, hard work, and passion were clear in every moment of the performance. We couldn’t be prouder of them!<br><br>🙌A heartfelt thank you goes to our amazing Expressive Arts Teacher, Mrs. McGraw, whose tireless efforts and creativity brought this production to life. <br><br> 🎶Here’s to another year of joy, unity, and celebration through the arts! <br><br>#nativity #christmasevent #esf #hongkong #primaryschool</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/27373b111a565f05545ec69aac58864f.jpg" alt="612954065_17987457965931900_3470628231600947479_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="127">
                        <time>06/01/2026</time>
                        <h3>✨ From Ideas To Impact ✨<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>💡Our Year 5 students brought their ‘How We Organise Ourselves’ Unit of Inquiry to life by planning, organising, and running their very own sustainable businesses! <br><br>The market had the following items: <br>🍴 Delicious food stalls<br>🎨 Origami & handmade crafts<br>🎲 Fun student-led activities<br><br>❤️Every dollar earned was donated to the Hong Kong Government Fund to support those affected by the Tai Po Fires.<br><br>🌍This market wasn’t just about cost, profit, and sustainability—it was about compassion, creativity, and community. <br><br>#marketday #communityimpact #primaryschool #hongkong</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/7d4f0a8977ed3f18f7e5aafa0831d8ff.jpg" alt="610768405_1270254531529255_4838697859439656628_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="126">
                        <time>26/11/2025</time>
                        <h3>☀️Peak School Year 5 = Adventure Mode ON!🌞<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>🌿Under perfect sunny skies, our students set off to the Wong Siu Sang Scout Camping Site, buzzing with excitement. <br><br>✨The fresh breeze and golden sunshine made every challenge feel like a celebration. <br><br>🧗‍♀️From soaring across the high ropes to conquering the climbing wall, they showed fearless bravery and unstoppable teamwork. <br><br>💪Echoes of laughter and cheers filled the camp, proving that courage grows stronger when shared. <br><br>💚By the end of the day, Year 5 didn’t just tackle obstacles—they built memories and friendships that shine as bright as the sun overhead. <br><br>📚Stay connected with us! ✨Follow @peakschoolhk to catch up on our students’ daily adventures & stay informed about all the exciting events happening at our school.<br><br>#scoutcamp #year5adventure #saikung #hongkong</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/d9c29a9f356f2027cdd52b7c35eae9f8.jpg" alt="584401127_17982393722931900_638207956645285281_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="125">
                        <time>17/11/2025</time>
                        <h3>Peak School was delighted to host the Year 1 Roles & Responsibilities Conference 2024! 🎉 <br>.<br>.<br>.<br>👩‍🏫Our curious Year 1 students eagerly joined their chosen mini-conferences, moving between sessions to discover and ask questions about the many important roles within our school.<br><br>📚From teachers and office staff to our hardworking caretaker and supportive PTA Chairman, each shared how they contribute to the success of our community. <br><br>🙌A big thank you to all Peak School staff for making this engaging and meaningful experience possible for our Year 1 learners!<br><br>📚Stay connected with us! ✨Follow @peakschoolhk to catch up on our students’ daily adventures & stay informed about all the exciting events happening at our school.<br><br>#rolesandresponsibilities #year1conference #esf #hongkong</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/0131d1e3d50a5e70098d659c3eb90403.jpg" alt="581683181_17981488307931900_2711099661500036365_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="124">
                        <time>13/11/2025</time>
                        <h3>📸 Over the past 3 days, Peak School turned on the charm for class and individual photos!<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>💫From sparkly shoes to standout accessories, everyone brought their A-game. <br><br>👯‍♂️ Sibling shots? Absolutely adorable. And catching the perfect moment for those goofy class photos? A true art form.<br><br>😂 Now it’s your turn! Comment below and tell us which class pulled the best funny faces!<br><br>📚Stay connected with us! ✨Follow @peakschoolhk to catch up on our students’ daily adventures & stay informed about all the exciting events happening at our school.<br><br>#schoolphotoshoot #funnyfaces #primaryschool #hongkong #esf</h3>
                        <button>Read more</button>
                        <img src="/cache/img/edac4a3d124922dd5c20c8e18c58f7f4.jpg" alt="581081780_17981069108931900_779726048686859908_n" loading="lazy" width="682" height="682" />                    </div>
                </div>
                            <div class="post-item">
                    <div class="post" data-id="123">
                        <time>05/11/2025</time>
