                                                    <h3>🍕 Farm-to-Table Fun! 🌱<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>🌾Our Year 3 Peakies had an unforgettable day at the New Zealand Organic Farm in Lam Tseun! <br><br>🍅From harvesting fresh organic veggies straight from the garden to kneading their very own pizza dough, the kids got hands-on with every step of the process. <br><br>✨The best part? Creating delicious pizzas topped with the greens they picked themselves. <br><br>🌿What a wholesome, tasty adventure!<br><br>#schooltrip #farmtotable #pizzamaking #hongkong #esf</h3>
