                    <time>17/11/2025</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>Peak School was delighted to host the Year 1 Roles & Responsibilities Conference 2024! 🎉 <br>.<br>.<br>.<br>👩‍🏫Our curious Year 1 students eagerly joined their chosen mini-conferences, moving between sessions to discover and ask questions about the many important roles within our school.<br><br>📚From teachers and office staff to our hardworking caretaker and supportive PTA Chairman, each shared how they contribute to the success of our community. <br><br>🙌A big thank you to all Peak School staff for making this engaging and meaningful experience possible for our Year 1 learners!<br><br>📚Stay connected with us! ✨Follow @peakschoolhk to catch up on our students’ daily adventures & stay informed about all the exciting events happening at our school.<br><br>#rolesandresponsibilities #year1conference #esf #hongkong</h3>
