            <div class="lightbox" data-id="123">
            <div class="lightbox-wrapper">
                <button class="close"></button>
                <div class="lightbox-container">
                    <time>05/11/2025</time>
                    <div class="lightbox-content">
                                                    <h3>Peak students in Year 4 and Year 5 were given a wonderful opportunity to connect with the remarkable Onjali Q. Raúf, a gifted and award-winning children’s author and activist, through a virtual session! <br><br>👦During this special time, she shared insights from her book, “The Boy at the Back of the Class.” Her stories truly resonate with young readers, helping them understand and navigate important issues in a way that feels both engaging and relatable. <br><br>🥹It’s heartwarming to see how her work inspires kids to embrace empathy and awareness in today’s world.<br><br>📚Stay connected with us! ✨Follow @peakschoolhk to catch up on our students’ daily adventures & stay informed about all the exciting events happening at our school.<br><br>#authorvisit #esf #primaryschool #hongkong</h3>
                                                                            <div class="gallery">
